1
00:00:07,807 --> 00:00:09,075
Where did this brat come from?

2
00:00:09,109 --> 00:00:10,943
How dare you steal from
the Crown Prince's camp?

3
00:00:10,944 --> 00:00:11,944
Beat him!

4
00:00:12,712 --> 00:00:13,712
Beat him to death!

5
00:00:14,047 --> 00:00:15,047
Beat him to death!

6
00:00:16,783 --> 00:00:17,783
For stealing!

7
00:00:20,086 --> 00:00:21,086
I'll kill you!

8
00:00:23,990 --> 00:00:24,990
Wait!

9
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:27,500
Greetings, Crown Prince.

10
00:00:27,900 --> 00:00:29,499
Some beggar from who knows where...

11
00:00:29,500 --> 00:00:30,999
sneaked in here to steal steamed buns.

12
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:32,360
He deserves to be beaten to death.

13
00:00:48,515 --> 00:00:49,515
Come here.

14
00:01:06,166 --> 00:01:06,700
Thank you.

15
00:01:06,966 --> 00:01:08,902
Thank you, Crown
Prince, for saving my life.

16
00:01:08,968 --> 00:01:10,170
Please take me in.

17
00:01:10,603 --> 00:01:12,181
I'll do anything as long as you
give me food to eat.

18
00:01:12,205 --> 00:01:13,406
I'll do whatever it takes.

19
00:01:20,814 --> 00:01:21,948
What's your name?

20
00:01:25,919 --> 00:01:26,919
Why?

21
00:01:27,354 --> 00:01:29,031
I've already gotten rid of
my third and fourth brothers,

22
00:01:29,055 --> 00:01:31,455
but Father still won't pass the
Crown Prince position to me.

23
00:01:54,114 --> 00:01:55,114
Your Highness,

24
00:01:56,349 --> 00:01:57,350
eat something sweet,

25
00:01:58,685 --> 00:02:00,005
and your mood won't be so gloomy.

26
00:02:04,290 --> 00:02:08,595
Do you think you can please
me with such petty tricks?

27
00:02:09,229 --> 00:02:10,663
I'm an orphan.

28
00:02:12,031 --> 00:02:13,509
I've endured all kinds of hardships
to survive since I was a child.

29
00:02:13,533 --> 00:02:14,533
I've suffered so much.

30
00:02:15,735 --> 00:02:16,936
But you took me in.

31
00:02:17,704 --> 00:02:18,704
From now on,

32
00:02:18,972 --> 00:02:20,473
I'm willing to live for you.

33
00:02:21,374 --> 00:02:22,609
As long as it makes you happy,

34
00:02:23,309 --> 00:02:24,544
I'll do anything.

35
00:02:45,398 --> 00:02:46,398
Your Highness,

36
00:02:47,333 --> 00:02:48,668
Have some hangover soup.

37
00:02:53,807 --> 00:02:54,807
Your Highness,

38
00:02:55,208 --> 00:02:56,543
I'm new to the imperial city.

39
00:02:57,310 --> 00:02:58,945
No one knows who I am.

40
00:03:00,313 --> 00:03:03,917
I want to transfer from being a gate guard

41
00:03:04,918 --> 00:03:06,453
to the Fifth Prince's Yunhe Palace

42
00:03:06,486 --> 00:03:08,221
and spy on his every move for you.

43
00:03:08,822 --> 00:03:09,822
If he has any improper ambitions

44
00:03:09,823 --> 00:03:11,023
for the Crown Prince position,

45
00:03:11,091 --> 00:03:13,426
I will report to you immediately.

46
00:03:15,228 --> 00:03:16,228
Very well.

47
00:03:16,930 --> 00:03:18,210
Since you have the heart for it,

48
00:03:19,165 --> 00:03:20,700
then stay by Yin Qi's side.

49
00:03:22,235 --> 00:03:23,235
Do a good job.

50
00:03:24,337 --> 00:03:26,206
I won't let you down, Your Highness.

51
00:03:26,973 --> 00:03:28,493
When you ascend to the Eastern Palace,

52
00:03:28,942 --> 00:03:29,942
I...

53
00:03:30,844 --> 00:03:32,512
will be able to...

54
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:35,315
return to your side openly.

55
00:04:58,300 --> 00:05:02,300
"Journey With You"

56
00:05:03,700 --> 00:05:05,700
(Episode 5)

57
00:05:06,673 --> 00:05:07,673
I wonder,

58
00:05:08,241 --> 00:05:09,709
could you give me a guarantee

59
00:05:11,277 --> 00:05:12,545
to make me believe

60
00:05:13,813 --> 00:05:16,115
that you're truly willing to
help me achieve my wishes?

61
00:05:32,232 --> 00:05:33,232
It's so late.

62
00:05:34,968 --> 00:05:35,968
Where have you been?

63
00:05:40,373 --> 00:05:41,373
I thought

64
00:05:41,541 --> 00:05:42,541
you trusted me

65
00:05:43,176 --> 00:05:44,976
and wouldn't associate
with Yin Zhou anymore.

66
00:05:45,645 --> 00:05:46,645
But why

67
00:05:46,980 --> 00:05:48,181
are you still going to him?

68
00:05:52,418 --> 00:05:54,120
I'm just a lowly hostage.

69
00:05:55,321 --> 00:05:56,521
I can't make my own decisions.

70
00:05:57,824 --> 00:05:58,824
It's all because.

71
00:05:59,792 --> 00:06:01,512
I have to follow the orders of you princes.

72
00:06:02,061 --> 00:06:03,061
Yanzhi,

73
00:06:03,663 --> 00:06:04,663
let me ask you,

74
00:06:05,465 --> 00:06:07,267
no matter how hard I try to keep you,

75
00:06:08,167 --> 00:06:09,469
you'll still work for Yin Zhou?

76
00:06:12,739 --> 00:06:14,574
I'm not only a hostage in the Daxing Palace

77
00:06:15,808 --> 00:06:17,143
but also a prince of Talhan.

78
00:06:18,611 --> 00:06:19,611
Yin Zhou

79
00:06:20,213 --> 00:06:22,215
is very likely to be the
future emperor of Daxing.

80
00:06:23,216 --> 00:06:24,216
Working for him

81
00:06:24,984 --> 00:06:25,984
what's wrong with that?

82
00:06:27,854 --> 00:06:29,455
If you're determined not to turn back,

83
00:06:30,623 --> 00:06:31,623
then

84
00:06:32,225 --> 00:06:33,545
we're no longer on the same path.

85
00:06:40,633 --> 00:06:41,633
Then, Fifth Prince,

86
00:06:42,535 --> 00:06:43,535
farewell.

87
00:07:08,995 --> 00:07:10,430
Could it be that they've already...

88
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:24,477
I'm the only one who can
make the decisions for you.

89
00:07:27,580 --> 00:07:28,847
It seems A Qi has really misunderstood

90
00:07:28,848 --> 00:07:30,183
my relationship with Yin Zhou.

91
00:07:31,417 --> 00:07:32,417
Well, never mind.

92
00:07:42,061 --> 00:07:42,895
Your Highness,

93
00:07:42,896 --> 00:07:44,630
haven't you been resting properly lately?

94
00:07:45,231 --> 00:07:46,871
This wound keeps reopening after healing.

95
00:07:47,166 --> 00:07:48,668
Don't you want this arm anymore?

96
00:07:50,236 --> 00:07:51,904
What has Yanzhi been doing lately?

97
00:07:52,772 --> 00:07:54,292
I haven't seen him around for a while.

98
00:07:55,375 --> 00:07:56,495
There's definitely something

99
00:07:56,709 --> 00:07:57,877
going on between them.

100
00:07:58,845 --> 00:08:00,847
Your Highness should
take care of your body.

101
00:08:01,748 --> 00:08:04,150
Nowadays,
our relationship with Talhan is uncertain.

102
00:08:04,884 --> 00:08:07,019
You're being so open
and sincere with the prince,

103
00:08:08,888 --> 00:08:09,888
but in the future,

104
00:08:09,989 --> 00:08:11,023
if something goes wrong,

105
00:08:11,891 --> 00:08:13,126
how will you handle it?

106
00:08:15,828 --> 00:08:16,828
Nanxing,

107
00:08:17,263 --> 00:08:18,383
thank you for your kindness,

108
00:08:19,599 --> 00:08:20,599
but

109
00:08:21,067 --> 00:08:21,934
I've been doing something
with Yanzhi lately

110
00:08:21,968 --> 00:08:24,203
that can't be known by outsiders.

111
00:08:26,472 --> 00:08:27,472
Don't worry,

112
00:08:27,940 --> 00:08:29,260
I'll definitely rest and recover.

113
00:08:34,414 --> 00:08:34,847
Your Highness,

114
00:08:35,248 --> 00:08:35,715
Well?

115
00:08:35,748 --> 00:08:36,349
Did you follow him?

116
00:08:36,649 --> 00:08:37,689
Forgive me, Your Highness.

117
00:08:37,850 --> 00:08:39,851
I still couldn't find out

118
00:08:39,852 --> 00:08:41,154
the prince's whereabouts today.

119
00:08:41,554 --> 00:08:42,088
Also,

120
00:08:42,488 --> 00:08:43,990
Duan Yi said the Crown Prince

121
00:08:44,023 --> 00:08:46,092
has also been missing all day lately.

122
00:08:47,460 --> 00:08:48,460
I see.

123
00:08:48,694 --> 00:08:49,694
You may leave now.

124
00:08:50,563 --> 00:08:51,723
This subordinate takes leave.

125
00:08:56,068 --> 00:08:57,068
Your Highness,

126
00:08:57,804 --> 00:09:00,124
Lately, you've faced dangers
several times for the prince.

127
00:09:00,239 --> 00:09:01,307
Have you ever thought

128
00:09:02,408 --> 00:09:03,910
that he might be someone

129
00:09:03,943 --> 00:09:05,503
who could bring you danger at any time?

130
00:09:06,579 --> 00:09:07,579
But

131
00:09:08,881 --> 00:09:09,881
he's also

132
00:09:10,349 --> 00:09:11,349
the most special one.

133
00:09:25,364 --> 00:09:27,066
Your Highness must rest properly lately.

134
00:09:27,633 --> 00:09:28,701
This wound was poisoned,

135
00:09:28,734 --> 00:09:29,734
and it's hard to heal.

136
00:09:29,969 --> 00:09:32,305
If it keeps reopening
like this, it'll easily fester.

137
00:09:44,851 --> 00:09:45,851
This...

138
00:09:46,219 --> 00:09:47,386
is what Concubine Chen

139
00:09:47,854 --> 00:09:49,255
always missed—Longjing cakes.

140
00:09:49,956 --> 00:09:52,734
She always said the cooks in the
palace didn't make them authentically.

141
00:09:52,758 --> 00:09:54,169
You've always said since you were a child

142
00:09:54,193 --> 00:09:56,273
that you wanted to taste
authentic Jiangnan cuisine.

143
00:09:57,763 --> 00:09:58,883
Come and try it. Is it good?

144
00:10:00,433 --> 00:10:02,313
The prince has to take
care of so many princes.

145
00:10:02,568 --> 00:10:03,568
It's so tiring for you.

146
00:10:04,036 --> 00:10:05,596
You still remembered what I said before.

147
00:10:06,038 --> 00:10:07,038
It cant be easy.

148
00:10:16,048 --> 00:10:17,208
Come and take a walk with me.

149
00:10:22,989 --> 00:10:23,989
I thought

150
00:10:24,257 --> 00:10:26,525
we had cleared the air
that night at Zhou Bridge.

151
00:10:27,260 --> 00:10:28,260
But why

152
00:10:29,695 --> 00:10:31,055
do you come close to me one moment

153
00:10:32,431 --> 00:10:33,871
and then distance yourself the next?

154
00:10:37,069 --> 00:10:38,069
A Qi,

155
00:10:38,738 --> 00:10:39,738
I...

156
00:10:41,574 --> 00:10:42,574
I'm sorry.

157
00:10:43,643 --> 00:10:44,877
I was too impulsive that day.

158
00:10:47,013 --> 00:10:48,013
One day,

159
00:10:48,614 --> 00:10:50,174
you'll marry your own princess consort.

160
00:10:51,751 --> 00:10:53,219
I shouldn't be an obstacle to you.

161
00:10:56,081 --> 00:10:57,883
Didn't you know I was
a prince from the start?

162
00:10:58,491 --> 00:10:59,358
I'm not afraid.

163
00:10:59,392 --> 00:11:00,392
What are you afraid of?

164
00:11:05,498 --> 00:11:06,498
Yanzhi,

165
00:11:07,767 --> 00:11:08,401
I've never asked you

166
00:11:08,401 --> 00:11:09,401
for any promises.

167
00:11:10,469 --> 00:11:12,672
I just hope you won't push me away anymore.

168
00:11:13,439 --> 00:11:14,673
Just this small request.

169
00:11:14,674 --> 00:11:15,674
Can't you grant it?

170
00:11:17,243 --> 00:11:18,277
The gap in our statuses

171
00:11:19,045 --> 00:11:20,112
is like heaven and earth.

172
00:11:22,148 --> 00:11:24,216
I can't just ignore everything

173
00:11:25,551 --> 00:11:26,685
and stand by your side without a care.

174
00:11:26,686 --> 00:11:27,686
Enough!

175
00:11:28,554 --> 00:11:30,114
You're sure I won't do anything to you,

176
00:11:30,589 --> 00:11:32,425
so you keep hurting me without restraint.

177
00:11:33,392 --> 00:11:35,728
We really can't seem to communicate.

178
00:11:42,234 --> 00:11:45,438
Did Yin Qi and Pei Yanzhi
really have a falling out?

179
00:11:46,639 --> 00:11:48,941
Could it be just childish temper tantrums,

180
00:11:49,542 --> 00:11:51,944
and they'll be inseparable
again in a few days?

181
00:11:52,778 --> 00:11:54,012
This subordinate truly

182
00:11:54,013 --> 00:11:56,082
heard Yin Qi say harsh words to Pei Yanzhi.

183
00:11:56,816 --> 00:11:58,417
Even if it's not a complete breakup,

184
00:11:59,285 --> 00:12:00,486
it's still serious.

185
00:12:02,622 --> 00:12:07,093
I don't care about their
closeness or distance whatsoever.

186
00:12:08,561 --> 00:12:09,561
But seeing Yin Qi

187
00:12:09,562 --> 00:12:11,230
upset because of Pei Yanzhi.

188
00:12:12,498 --> 00:12:13,966
I am quite pleased.

189
00:12:16,569 --> 00:12:18,104
I heard from De Shun

190
00:12:18,404 --> 00:12:20,604
that Father is hosting a
banquet at Yanbo Tower tonight

191
00:12:21,607 --> 00:12:23,876
and has invited Yin Qi and
Yin Heshu to accompany him.

192
00:12:26,879 --> 00:12:27,947
This old fox.

193
00:12:29,248 --> 00:12:30,750
He's been favoring Yin Qi lately

194
00:12:31,017 --> 00:12:32,018
and ignoring me.

195
00:12:32,752 --> 00:12:34,954
He wants to reprimand me like this.

196
00:12:36,822 --> 00:12:37,822
Yanbo Tower.

197
00:12:38,290 --> 00:12:39,125
Your Highness,

198
00:12:39,191 --> 00:12:40,859
didn't you also arrange

199
00:12:40,860 --> 00:12:42,620
to meet Pei Yanzhi and
Su He at Yanbo Tower?

200
00:12:47,033 --> 00:12:48,501
Yanbo Tower

201
00:12:49,635 --> 00:12:50,970
will be the stage

202
00:12:51,837 --> 00:12:53,372
for Pei Yanzhi and Yin Qi

203
00:12:54,340 --> 00:12:56,976
to have a complete falling out.

204
00:13:04,850 --> 00:13:05,850
Yanbo Tower.

205
00:13:06,652 --> 00:13:08,587
Yanbo Tower is very famous in Jiangnan.

206
00:13:08,687 --> 00:13:09,622
The owner is very mysterious.

207
00:13:09,655 --> 00:13:12,291
It's said that his businesses
are all over the Central Plains.

208
00:13:12,992 --> 00:13:14,293
It seems Yanbo Tower

209
00:13:15,227 --> 00:13:17,387
is connected to the Piaoxiang
Pavilion in the capital.

210
00:13:18,898 --> 00:13:20,566
Yanzhi is acting so strangely today.

211
00:13:22,735 --> 00:13:24,470
He must be meeting someone at Yanbo Tower.

212
00:13:24,837 --> 00:13:25,837
Your Highness,

213
00:13:26,539 --> 00:13:28,407
Then we...

214
00:13:30,876 --> 00:13:31,876
Fifth Prince,

215
00:13:31,977 --> 00:13:34,413
His Majesty instructed
this old servant to tell you

216
00:13:34,747 --> 00:13:36,949
that he's hosting a banquet
at Yanbo Tower tonight

217
00:13:37,283 --> 00:13:39,418
and has invited you and
Sixth Princess to attend.

218
00:13:41,220 --> 00:13:42,455
Just the two of us siblings?

219
00:13:42,955 --> 00:13:43,456
Yes.

220
00:13:43,956 --> 00:13:46,492
His Majesty said Yanbo
Tower has beautiful scenery

221
00:13:46,692 --> 00:13:49,528
and it was Concubine Chen's
favorite restaurant when she was alive.

222
00:13:49,862 --> 00:13:52,498
So he only invited you and Sixth Princess.

223
00:13:53,099 --> 00:13:53,399
Okay.

224
00:13:53,632 --> 00:13:54,233
I understand.

225
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:55,434
You may leave now.

226
00:13:55,468 --> 00:13:55,735
Yes.

227
00:13:55,968 --> 00:13:57,128
This old servant takes leave.

228
00:14:04,076 --> 00:14:05,076
Your Highness,

229
00:14:05,411 --> 00:14:06,278
Why would the Emperor

230
00:14:06,279 --> 00:14:07,713
invite you to Yanbo Tower alone?

231
00:14:07,747 --> 00:14:09,107
Could he have found out something?

232
00:14:09,815 --> 00:14:11,150
Judging by De Shun's demeanor,

233
00:14:11,951 --> 00:14:13,662
Father is probably just
inviting us to Yanbo Tower

234
00:14:13,686 --> 00:14:15,187
for a simple banquet.

235
00:14:15,254 --> 00:14:16,254
Nothing else.

236
00:14:17,356 --> 00:14:20,559
What about the person the
prince is secretly meeting?

237
00:14:21,627 --> 00:14:22,828
No matter who it is tonight,

238
00:14:23,095 --> 00:14:24,630
we must be extremely careful.

239
00:14:25,631 --> 00:14:26,631
Duan Yong.

240
00:14:26,766 --> 00:14:28,033
Come with me to Yanbo Tower.

241
00:14:28,667 --> 00:14:29,667
Ziming.

242
00:14:31,036 --> 00:14:32,116
Let him rest for the night.

243
00:14:33,239 --> 00:14:34,239
Yes, Your Highness.

244
00:14:35,574 --> 00:14:36,574
Oh well.

245
00:14:36,976 --> 00:14:37,976
Take Ziming with us.

246
00:14:39,879 --> 00:14:42,081
This chess piece arranged by Elder Brother

247
00:14:44,049 --> 00:14:46,152
It's time to play its part.

248
00:14:47,586 --> 00:14:48,586
Ziming?

249
00:14:49,054 --> 00:14:50,054
How could it be?

250
00:14:51,157 --> 00:14:52,291
It's really unexpected.

251
00:14:52,458 --> 00:14:53,692
Treat him just like before.

252
00:14:54,059 --> 00:14:55,361
Don't show any flaws.

253
00:14:56,428 --> 00:14:57,428
Yes, Your Highness.

254
00:15:01,500 --> 00:15:02,500
Farewell, sir.

255
00:15:07,106 --> 00:15:08,106
Come in, sir.

256
00:15:12,244 --> 00:15:13,244
Please sit here.

257
00:15:13,746 --> 00:15:14,213
Senior.

258
00:15:14,613 --> 00:15:16,525
Today, we'd like to use the
Jinling Spring private room.

259
00:15:16,549 --> 00:15:18,026
We have important matters to discuss.

260
00:15:18,050 --> 00:15:19,050
Okay.

261
00:15:19,985 --> 00:15:20,419
Xianyue,

262
00:15:20,820 --> 00:15:21,820
take them there.

263
00:15:21,987 --> 00:15:22,987
Be careful.

264
00:15:52,351 --> 00:15:53,552
My dear nephew.

265
00:15:57,690 --> 00:16:00,793
You've suffered in Daxing all these years.

266
00:16:01,660 --> 00:16:03,295
Now it's finally time

267
00:16:03,796 --> 00:16:05,836
for you and I, uncle and
nephew, to take the stage.

268
00:16:07,066 --> 00:16:08,066
Don't worry.

269
00:16:08,267 --> 00:16:09,267
After things are done,

270
00:16:10,202 --> 00:16:12,605
you'll have all the riches and honors.

271
00:16:13,572 --> 00:16:15,372
You won't have to endure
humiliation anymore,

272
00:16:15,474 --> 00:16:16,554
pretending to be a hostage.

273
00:16:18,277 --> 00:16:19,277
Uncle is joking.

274
00:16:19,745 --> 00:16:20,745
Riches and honors

275
00:16:21,146 --> 00:16:22,815
are just fleeting clouds to me.

276
00:16:23,249 --> 00:16:24,249
What I truly care about

277
00:16:24,650 --> 00:16:26,210
is the rise and fall of our grasslands.

278
00:16:27,119 --> 00:16:27,453
By the way,

279
00:16:28,087 --> 00:16:29,087
the Fifth Prince

280
00:16:29,321 --> 00:16:30,321
has been kind to me.

281
00:16:30,623 --> 00:16:31,490
When the time comes,

282
00:16:31,491 --> 00:16:32,851
I've agreed with the eldest prince

283
00:16:33,192 --> 00:16:34,272
that after things are done,

284
00:16:34,360 --> 00:16:36,520
he'll be allowed to live a
life of leisure and wealth.

285
00:16:37,563 --> 00:16:39,365
A proud prince of the grasslands

286
00:16:39,832 --> 00:16:41,867
can't be trapped by love and affection.

287
00:16:42,735 --> 00:16:44,970
You should look further ahead.

288
00:16:48,908 --> 00:16:49,808
If you really like

289
00:16:49,809 --> 00:16:52,311
that fair-skinned prince of Daxing,

290
00:16:53,279 --> 00:16:54,279
when the time comes,

291
00:16:54,813 --> 00:16:56,333
just bring him back to the grasslands.

292
00:16:57,216 --> 00:16:58,216
Uncle

293
00:16:58,317 --> 00:16:59,317
approves.

294
00:17:01,754 --> 00:17:03,274
In terms of great talent and strategy,

295
00:17:03,389 --> 00:17:05,029
I definitely can't compare to you, Uncle.

296
00:17:06,058 --> 00:17:07,126
The Crown Prince.

297
00:17:07,159 --> 00:17:07,960
He'll come later.

298
00:17:08,160 --> 00:17:09,600
He ordered me to entertain you well.

299
00:17:09,928 --> 00:17:10,928
Please.

300
00:17:20,039 --> 00:17:21,359
This meat from the Central Plains

301
00:17:21,774 --> 00:17:23,534
is far inferior to ours
from the grasslands.

302
00:17:24,243 --> 00:17:25,643
It seems Uncle has made up his mind

303
00:17:26,045 --> 00:17:27,125
to assist the eldest prince

304
00:17:27,846 --> 00:17:28,948
in achieving his goals.

305
00:17:30,949 --> 00:17:33,686
The queen has a vast
network of power in the court.

306
00:17:34,153 --> 00:17:35,254
She has deep roots.

307
00:17:36,388 --> 00:17:39,391
If I become a core member
of the crown prince's faction,

308
00:17:40,159 --> 00:17:42,995
there will definitely be
benefits for me in the future.

309
00:17:43,562 --> 00:17:44,763
The crown prince

310
00:17:44,997 --> 00:17:46,799
can give this Khan what I need.

311
00:17:47,566 --> 00:17:48,901
Helping him ascend to the throne,

312
00:17:50,069 --> 00:17:51,503
why wouldn't I help?

313
00:18:00,446 --> 00:18:02,286
The Concubine Chen's
skill in playing the qin.

314
00:18:02,348 --> 00:18:03,615
Heshu has learned a bit of it.

315
00:18:03,682 --> 00:18:05,150
She’s somewhat decent.

316
00:18:07,052 --> 00:18:08,854
Qi'er, do you know?

317
00:18:09,188 --> 00:18:10,489
Your mother back then

318
00:18:11,023 --> 00:18:12,524
also liked Yanbo Tower very much.

319
00:18:15,094 --> 00:18:17,196
The way Sixth Princess
sits and plays the qin

320
00:18:17,830 --> 00:18:19,932
reminds this old servant
of the Concubine Chen.

321
00:18:24,803 --> 00:18:25,803
Father.

322
00:18:26,772 --> 00:18:28,240
I've told you many times.

323
00:18:28,374 --> 00:18:29,208
I'm now

324
00:18:29,274 --> 00:18:31,477
just an ordinary wealthy merchant.

325
00:18:33,579 --> 00:18:34,579
I'm used to it.

326
00:18:35,013 --> 00:18:36,013
Father.

327
00:18:36,782 --> 00:18:38,917
The scenery at Yanbo Tower is really nice.

328
00:18:39,385 --> 00:18:41,225
It's different from the
bustle of the capital.

329
00:18:41,453 --> 00:18:43,288
Jiangnan is small and elegant.

330
00:18:43,822 --> 00:18:45,090
It's quite charming.

331
00:18:47,459 --> 00:18:48,459
Here.

332
00:18:49,695 --> 00:18:50,796
Let me toast you, Father.

333
00:19:02,141 --> 00:19:03,141
Oh, Father.

334
00:19:04,009 --> 00:19:05,477
I've heard that Yanbo Tower

335
00:19:06,211 --> 00:19:07,646
has many seasonal Jiangnan dishes.

336
00:19:08,047 --> 00:19:09,527
I'll go to the kitchen to take a look

337
00:19:09,782 --> 00:19:11,259
and see what fresh dishes are available

338
00:19:11,283 --> 00:19:12,963
so that Father can enjoy a delicious meal.

339
00:19:13,986 --> 00:19:15,666
It's rare that you have such filial piety.

340
00:19:16,055 --> 00:19:17,055
Go quickly.

341
00:19:26,298 --> 00:19:27,298
Aunt,

342
00:19:27,433 --> 00:19:29,193
you've been standing
here for quite a while.

343
00:19:29,268 --> 00:19:31,904
Is the girl's piano
playing really that good?

344
00:19:36,208 --> 00:19:37,743
The piece she's playing

345
00:19:38,243 --> 00:19:40,712
lacks some of the freedom her mother had,

346
00:19:41,413 --> 00:19:42,748
but adds a touch of playfulness.

347
00:19:43,248 --> 00:19:44,650
You're not saying that

348
00:19:44,783 --> 00:19:47,064
they are the children of your
old acquaintances, are you?

349
00:19:50,456 --> 00:19:51,456
She...

350
00:19:57,763 --> 00:19:58,763
Your Highness,

351
00:19:59,498 --> 00:20:00,833
I just saw that

352
00:20:01,066 --> 00:20:02,744
the young master entered a private room
opposite Yanbo Tower

353
00:20:02,768 --> 00:20:04,369
with a foreigner,

354
00:20:05,003 --> 00:20:06,003
presumably

355
00:20:06,605 --> 00:20:08,006
to meet with his clansmen.

356
00:20:09,208 --> 00:20:10,676
If I'm not mistaken,

357
00:20:11,210 --> 00:20:12,210
that foreigner

358
00:20:12,311 --> 00:20:13,312
is his uncle.

359
00:20:14,446 --> 00:20:15,280
Yanzhi has been

360
00:20:15,281 --> 00:20:16,615
working for Yin Zhou and Su He.

361
00:20:16,982 --> 00:20:18,359
I tried to persuade him with kind words,

362
00:20:18,383 --> 00:20:19,585
but I couldn't stop him.

363
00:20:20,819 --> 00:20:21,963
Whether he lives or dies in the future

364
00:20:21,987 --> 00:20:23,267
will have nothing to do with me.

365
00:20:24,223 --> 00:20:25,223
Your Highness,

366
00:20:25,624 --> 00:20:26,624
you and the young master

367
00:20:27,626 --> 00:20:29,261
have had a ten-year friendship.

368
00:20:29,495 --> 00:20:30,495
So what?

369
00:20:30,863 --> 00:20:31,730
Hasn't he still been secretly working

370
00:20:31,763 --> 00:20:32,898
for Yin Zhou behind my back?

371
00:20:33,966 --> 00:20:34,966
Ziming,

372
00:20:35,267 --> 00:20:37,336
from now on, you don't need to report

373
00:20:37,369 --> 00:20:38,780
any news about Yanzhi and Yin Zhou to me.

374
00:20:38,804 --> 00:20:39,964
It has nothing to do with me.

375
00:20:50,949 --> 00:20:51,350
Father,

376
00:20:51,683 --> 00:20:52,417
I've arranged everything.

377
00:20:52,651 --> 00:20:53,651
Good.

378
00:20:53,986 --> 00:20:54,319
Come.

379
00:20:54,586 --> 00:20:55,586
Let's drink.

380
00:21:01,360 --> 00:21:02,360
Dear guests,

381
00:21:02,761 --> 00:21:04,129
I'm the owner of the Yanbo Tower.

382
00:21:04,897 --> 00:21:07,417
I see that you distinguished
guests have extraordinary bearing.

383
00:21:07,666 --> 00:21:08,066
From now on,

384
00:21:08,433 --> 00:21:10,202
please take care of our business.

385
00:21:11,370 --> 00:21:13,205
This is Jinlingchun presented by our shop.

386
00:21:13,805 --> 00:21:15,107
Please have a taste.

387
00:21:17,075 --> 00:21:18,577
Is it brewed by the wine shop

388
00:21:18,610 --> 00:21:20,345
across from the Yanbo Tower?

389
00:21:20,846 --> 00:21:21,846
Exactly.

390
00:21:22,247 --> 00:21:23,115
This distinguished guest,

391
00:21:23,148 --> 00:21:24,148
you look unfamiliar.

392
00:21:24,583 --> 00:21:27,023
And your accent doesn't sound like
that of a Jiangnan person.

393
00:21:27,085 --> 00:21:28,520
Yet you're so knowledgeable.

394
00:21:29,254 --> 00:21:32,391
You must be a big shot who
has seen a lot of the world.

395
00:21:39,631 --> 00:21:40,666
Back then, your mother

396
00:21:41,433 --> 00:21:42,568
sat right in this seat,

397
00:21:43,068 --> 00:21:46,471
playing the same tune that
Heshu just played on the qin.

398
00:21:47,439 --> 00:21:49,439
I didn't expect that after
she finished the piece,

399
00:21:50,008 --> 00:21:51,048
she picked up her wine cup

400
00:21:51,076 --> 00:21:52,878
and took a sip of this Jinlingchun.

401
00:21:53,845 --> 00:21:56,181
I never thought that

402
00:21:56,415 --> 00:21:57,883
such a gentle Jiangnan woman

403
00:21:58,283 --> 00:22:00,519
would have such a bold side.

404
00:22:04,656 --> 00:22:05,657
In the blink of an eye,

405
00:22:07,025 --> 00:22:09,261
it's been twenty years

406
00:22:09,995 --> 00:22:11,897
since I first met your mother.

407
00:22:18,170 --> 00:22:19,438
Look at your son and daughter.

408
00:22:19,771 --> 00:22:21,240
They're so handsome and beautiful.

409
00:22:21,974 --> 00:22:23,374
I bet your wife

410
00:22:23,375 --> 00:22:25,010
must also be a great beauty.

411
00:22:27,079 --> 00:22:28,079
We in Jiangnan

412
00:22:28,247 --> 00:22:29,314
had a famous beauty

413
00:22:29,948 --> 00:22:31,950
twenty years ago

414
00:22:33,485 --> 00:22:34,286
named.

415
00:22:34,287 --> 00:22:35,487
Su Tang'er.

416
00:22:36,555 --> 00:22:37,555
What?

417
00:22:38,123 --> 00:22:39,157
Do you know her?

418
00:22:45,097 --> 00:22:46,097
I've heard that

419
00:22:46,265 --> 00:22:48,743
she later entered the palace
and became an imperial concubine.

420
00:22:48,767 --> 00:22:50,702
Such a heavenly beauty

421
00:22:51,670 --> 00:22:54,271
is not someone a vulgar person like me

422
00:22:54,272 --> 00:22:55,507
could ever get to know.

423
00:22:56,842 --> 00:22:58,043
I think

424
00:22:58,443 --> 00:22:59,344
you,

425
00:22:59,344 --> 00:23:00,344
a woman,

426
00:23:00,779 --> 00:23:02,613
can run such a big tavern so well.

427
00:23:02,614 --> 00:23:04,216
You must be an outstanding person.

428
00:23:05,050 --> 00:23:07,019
If the madam doesn't mind,

429
00:23:07,419 --> 00:23:07,953
would you like to

430
00:23:08,220 --> 00:23:10,422
have a drink with us tonight?

431
00:23:12,290 --> 00:23:13,290
My two children

432
00:23:13,792 --> 00:23:15,694
are also visiting
Jiangnan for the first time.

433
00:23:18,397 --> 00:23:20,999
Since Yanbo Tower seems to
have a fateful connection with you,

434
00:23:23,235 --> 00:23:24,736
I'll have a drink with you.

435
00:23:26,471 --> 00:23:27,471
Good.

436
00:23:29,675 --> 00:23:31,910
You're truly a heroine among women.

437
00:23:32,244 --> 00:23:32,644
Come.

438
00:23:33,045 --> 00:23:33,578
Sit down.

439
00:23:33,879 --> 00:23:34,879
Let's drink slowly.

440
00:23:36,415 --> 00:23:37,949
Thank you for your kind offer.

441
00:23:38,684 --> 00:23:39,718
But my little shop

442
00:23:39,751 --> 00:23:41,486
has a lot of things to take care of.

443
00:23:42,220 --> 00:23:43,388
I'll take my leave first.

444
00:24:03,975 --> 00:24:06,578
Has Father taken a fancy to this madam?

445
00:24:06,845 --> 00:24:07,845
Don't talk nonsense.

446
00:24:09,147 --> 00:24:11,350
I think this madam is
definitely not simple.

447
00:24:12,490 --> 00:24:13,490
Why?

448
00:24:14,386 --> 00:24:15,626
Don't worry about that for now.

449
00:24:18,356 --> 00:24:19,356
As your elder brother,

450
00:24:19,691 --> 00:24:20,691
I'll give you a task.

451
00:24:27,733 --> 00:24:28,733
Father,

452
00:24:29,067 --> 00:24:30,502
Such a nice place as Jiangnan,

453
00:24:30,769 --> 00:24:32,747
and this is the first time
you've brought us here.

454
00:24:32,771 --> 00:24:35,040
You should be punished
with this cup of wine, right?

455
00:24:35,273 --> 00:24:36,274
Okay, okay, okay.

456
00:24:36,675 --> 00:24:38,410
I deserve the punishment.

457
00:24:40,212 --> 00:24:41,279
This cup

458
00:24:41,680 --> 00:24:42,840
is from your daughter to you.

459
00:24:43,181 --> 00:24:45,416
You've been so good to mother and us.

460
00:24:45,417 --> 00:24:47,352
You're the best father in the world.

461
00:24:49,254 --> 00:24:50,254
Come on.

462
00:24:50,589 --> 00:24:52,256
Since Jinlingchun tastes so good,

463
00:24:52,257 --> 00:24:53,634
of course we should have another cup.

464
00:24:53,658 --> 00:24:54,192
You.

465
00:24:54,626 --> 00:24:55,961
Always teasing your father.

466
00:25:05,237 --> 00:25:06,237
By the way,

467
00:25:07,038 --> 00:25:08,604
Aruna is also fourteen
years old now, right?

468
00:25:08,722 --> 00:25:10,410
Is she doing well at uncle's place?

469
00:25:12,377 --> 00:25:13,377
She's doing great.

470
00:25:13,979 --> 00:25:14,979
Don't worry.

471
00:25:16,448 --> 00:25:17,516
It looks like

472
00:25:17,616 --> 00:25:18,816
she's approaching

473
00:25:18,817 --> 00:25:20,285
the age to get married.

474
00:25:21,019 --> 00:25:23,822
I've already found a
suitable candidate for her.

475
00:25:24,423 --> 00:25:25,957
The Khan of the western grasslands,

476
00:25:26,291 --> 00:25:27,291
Urhtu.

477
00:25:28,360 --> 00:25:29,360
Urhtu.

478
00:25:30,228 --> 00:25:31,508
Isn't he almost sixty years old?

479
00:25:34,032 --> 00:25:35,792
Even if uncle wants
to win over their tribe,

480
00:25:36,201 --> 00:25:37,035
he shouldn't make Aruna

481
00:25:37,036 --> 00:25:38,235
marry that old man.

482
00:25:38,236 --> 00:25:39,236
I don't agree with this.

483
00:25:41,973 --> 00:25:43,575
Your elder brother is incompetent.

484
00:25:44,209 --> 00:25:45,209
The whole Talhan tribe

485
00:25:46,344 --> 00:25:47,984
has to rely on me to take care of things.

486
00:25:50,649 --> 00:25:51,649
Fengsun,

487
00:25:53,184 --> 00:25:54,961
You've been living a
peaceful life in Daxing.

488
00:25:54,986 --> 00:25:56,388
You've gotten used to it.

489
00:25:57,355 --> 00:25:59,035
Have you forgotten that on the grasslands,

490
00:25:59,424 --> 00:26:01,459
one has to fight to survive?

491
00:26:01,484 --> 00:26:01,951
You.

492
00:26:01,979 --> 00:26:04,314
The Jinlingchun is right across the way.

493
00:26:04,496 --> 00:26:05,030
Back then,

494
00:26:05,297 --> 00:26:06,697
your mother and I

495
00:26:06,698 --> 00:26:07,966
often came here to buy wine.

496
00:26:10,161 --> 00:26:11,595
Khan, let me go have a look.

497
00:26:11,770 --> 00:26:12,971
After all these years,

498
00:26:13,605 --> 00:26:15,473
I wonder if there have been any changes.

499
00:26:16,241 --> 00:26:17,142
This bridge,

500
00:26:17,209 --> 00:26:19,443
your mother and I

501
00:26:19,444 --> 00:26:21,124
used to walk across it together back then.

502
00:26:21,446 --> 00:26:22,180
Excuse me, sir.

503
00:26:22,214 --> 00:26:22,948
I'm sorry,

504
00:26:22,981 --> 00:26:24,615
but the Jinlingchun is booked
for a private event today.

505
00:26:24,616 --> 00:26:26,016
We're not accepting outside guests.

506
00:26:27,252 --> 00:26:27,953
This place

507
00:26:27,986 --> 00:26:30,722
was where my wife and
I often came back to.

508
00:26:30,822 --> 00:26:32,958
So I thought I'd come back for a visit.

509
00:26:33,225 --> 00:26:34,493
It was rude of me.

510
00:26:36,361 --> 00:26:36,862
Father,

511
00:26:37,262 --> 00:26:39,464
We all know how devoted you are to mother.

512
00:26:40,031 --> 00:26:41,231
Then let's come back tomorrow.

513
00:26:41,633 --> 00:26:42,633
You.

514
00:26:43,201 --> 00:26:44,870
How dare you make fun of your father?

515
00:26:45,437 --> 00:26:46,437
You deserve a punishment.

516
00:26:47,005 --> 00:26:49,541
Then punish me by making me drink
with you every day.

517
00:26:52,477 --> 00:26:53,477
Okay.

518
00:26:54,412 --> 00:26:55,412
Let's go back.

519
00:27:05,423 --> 00:27:06,458
You Central Plains people

520
00:27:07,092 --> 00:27:08,927
are so cautious in your words.

521
00:27:09,628 --> 00:27:11,129
It's really annoying.

522
00:27:14,633 --> 00:27:15,633
The Crown Prince

523
00:27:16,134 --> 00:27:17,636
has deep roots in the court.

524
00:27:18,003 --> 00:27:19,003
That's true.

525
00:27:19,771 --> 00:27:20,771
But he relies on

526
00:27:21,039 --> 00:27:22,607
the maternal clan of the Empress.

527
00:27:23,041 --> 00:27:24,109
As far as I know,

528
00:27:24,643 --> 00:27:26,843
the Emperor has no intention of
sharing power with him.

529
00:27:27,245 --> 00:27:28,245
I'm afraid that

530
00:27:28,847 --> 00:27:29,981
if the Emperor's preference

531
00:27:30,015 --> 00:27:31,416
is not the Crown Prince,

532
00:27:31,983 --> 00:27:33,343
that Uncle has chosen the wrong person.

533
00:27:36,488 --> 00:27:38,156
Yin Zhao, that old fox,

534
00:27:38,990 --> 00:27:41,026
doesn't even trust his own son.

535
00:27:41,593 --> 00:27:43,228
What kind of hero is he?

536
00:27:45,630 --> 00:27:46,630
However,

537
00:27:47,699 --> 00:27:49,501
what do you mean by this?

538
00:27:50,602 --> 00:27:51,602
Back then,

539
00:27:51,803 --> 00:27:53,204
it was you who sent a secret envoy

540
00:27:53,471 --> 00:27:55,472
to ask for my help

541
00:27:55,473 --> 00:27:56,741
for the Crown Prince,

542
00:27:58,043 --> 00:28:02,146
So it was Yanzhi wo was behind inciting
Yin Zhou and Su He to rebel together.

543
00:28:02,948 --> 00:28:04,649
He's the one who started all this.

544
00:28:05,450 --> 00:28:06,450
How is that possible?

545
00:28:06,618 --> 00:28:08,253
Back then, I had the same idea as uncle.

546
00:28:08,887 --> 00:28:11,165
To help the Crown Prince ascend to
the position of Crown Prince.

547
00:28:11,189 --> 00:28:12,189
In this way,

548
00:28:12,390 --> 00:28:14,350
we could gain the upper
hand in the Daxing court.

549
00:28:14,693 --> 00:28:15,693
But recently,

550
00:28:16,194 --> 00:28:18,930
the Emperor has also shown great favor
to the Fifth Prince.

551
00:28:20,198 --> 00:28:21,332
If the Emperor's preference

552
00:28:21,333 --> 00:28:23,213
is for the Fifth Prince
to be the Crown Prince,

553
00:28:23,601 --> 00:28:24,903
it's also a possibility.

554
00:28:34,223 --> 00:28:39,951
You don't have to test my determination
on behalf of the Crown Prince.

555
00:28:41,086 --> 00:28:43,822
We grasslanders keep our word.

556
00:28:44,823 --> 00:28:45,490
Since.

557
00:28:45,790 --> 00:28:46,324
I, the Khan,

558
00:28:46,624 --> 00:28:49,327
have promised to cooperate
with the Crown Prince,

559
00:28:49,761 --> 00:28:51,041
I will never go back on my word.

560
00:29:12,512 --> 00:29:17,052
The crown prince has sent me to
deliver this message to the Khan's hands.

561
00:29:31,336 --> 00:29:32,469
It seems that I

562
00:29:32,470 --> 00:29:34,005
won't be able to see the.

