front and tigers behind.

574
00:30:07,338 --> 00:30:08,338
In a few days,

575
00:30:08,773 --> 00:30:11,509
I, the Khan, will set off back to Talhan.

576
00:30:12,610 --> 00:30:15,346
As for the Crown Prince,

577
00:30:15,447 --> 00:30:16,447
Uncle, don't worry.

578
00:30:16,981 --> 00:30:18,583
I won't let uncle's trip be in vain.

579
00:30:36,835 --> 00:30:38,236
I've been keeping an eye on Yin Qi.

580
00:30:38,870 --> 00:30:40,705
His expression hasn't changed at all.

581
00:30:41,372 --> 00:30:42,372
It seems that

582
00:30:42,874 --> 00:30:45,591
