Su He will only think that.

598
00:31:28,887 --> 00:31:30,288
I can't do without him.

599
00:31:49,774 --> 00:31:50,774
My lord,

600
00:31:52,043 --> 00:31:53,578
judging by what Fengsun said,

601
00:31:54,846 --> 00:31:56,314
the old Emperor of Daxing

602
