I, the Khan, already knew.

605
00:32:08,860 --> 00:32:11,329
Who becomes the Crown Prince in Daxing.

606
00:32:12,163 --> 00:32:12,697
I, the Khan,

607
00:32:13,064 --> 00:32:14,199
don't care at all.

608
00:32:15,166 --> 00:32:16,367
I only know that

609
00:32:17,335 --> 00:32:19,537
the more chaotic the Daxing court is,

610
00:32:20,038 --> 00:32:23,308
the more we can reap the benefits.

611
00:32:26,277 --> 00:32:28,947
If the Fifth Prince

612
00:32:29,847 --> 00:32:30,927
comes to cooperate with me,

613
00:32:31,382 --> 00:32:33,818
I, the Khan, will also consider it.

614
00:32:34,786 --> 00:32:35,786
My lord,

615
00:32:36,221 --> 00:32:37,222
What does this mean?

616
00:32:40,792 --> 00:32:45,129
Tiele Suhe gave the
military token to Fengsun.

617
00:32:46,297 --> 00:32:48,733
I, the Khan, came to Jiangnan this time

618
00:32:49,367 --> 00:32:51,669
because I wanted that
military token in his hand.

619
00:32:52,437 --> 00:32:53,437
I think.

620
00:32:53,838 --> 00:32:55,240
Yin Zhou can't wait any longer

621
00:32:55,640 --> 00:32:57,041
to ascend to the throne.

622
00:32:58,376 --> 00:33:00,278
As long as he makes a move,

623
00:33:00,878 --> 00:33:01,878
we can

624
00:33:02,293 --> 00:33:05,076
use his hands to get rid of Fengsun.

625
00:33:07,852 --> 00:33:10,054
My lord is truly far-sighted.

626
