To my lord.

627
00:33:33,011 --> 00:33:34,011
A Qi,

628
00:33:35,413 --> 00:33:36,413
what are you doing here?

629
00:33:38,950 --> 00:33:42,220
I thought you were forced to do things

630
00:33:42,787 --> 00:33:44,589
