were being threatened.

641
00:34:11,249 --> 00:34:12,249
Since

642
00:34:13,051 --> 00:34:14,886
you've already chosen to go against me,

643
00:34:16,287 --> 00:34:17,287
then,

644
00:34:23,061 --> 00:34:23,561
A Qi,

645
00:34:24,028 --> 00:34:25,028
A Qi,

646
00:34:26,264 --> 00:34:27,264
A Qi,

647
00:34:27,598 --> 00:34:28,733
listen to my explaination.

648
00:34:29,019 --> 00:34:30,096
Do you want everyone in the palace

649
00:34:30,134 --> 00:34:31,814
