650
00:34:34,038 --> 00:34:35,038
A Qi,

651
00:34:36,474 --> 00:34:37,809
A Qi, don't be like this.

652
00:34:38,176 --> 00:34:39,477
Why don't you just kill me?

653
00:34:39,944 --> 00:34:41,504
It would be better than all these years

654
00:34:41,646 --> 00:34:44,614
