enduring humiliation for your tribe.

655
00:34:45,683 --> 00:34:46,683
Can't do it?

656
00:34:48,186 --> 00:34:48,953
I'll help you.

657
00:34:48,986 --> 00:34:50,488
A Qi, calm down.

658
00:34:51,022 --> 00:34:52,523
I did this for a purpose.

659
00:34:52,690 --> 00:34:54,050
Things aren't like what you think.

660
00:34:54,592 --> 00:34:55,632
You should have known that

661
