697
00:36:36,761 --> 00:36:38,162
If I had to choose again,

698
00:36:39,230 --> 00:36:40,298
I would still do it.

699
00:36:48,339 --> 00:36:48,773
No.

700
00:36:49,240 --> 00:36:50,240
That's not right.

701
00:36:50,374 --> 00:36:51,374
In a past life,

702
00:36:51,509 --> 00:36:52,909
Yanzhi went to save the Emperor,

703
00:36:52,910 --> 00:36:53,911
not to kill him.

704
00:36:54,679 --> 00:36:55,446
So that's what happened.

705
00:36:55,446 --> 00:36:56,446
A Qi,

706
00:36:57,148 --> 00:36:58,708
As long as I plan everything carefully,

707
00:36:59,550 --> 00:37:00,550
